Object.Field: SELECT i.INDEX_NAME INDEX_NAME, k.COLUMN_NAME COLUMN_NAME FROM QSYS2.SYSKEYS k, QSYS2.SYSINDEXES i, QSYS2.SYSCOLUMNS c WHERE k.INDEX_SCHEMA=i.INDEX_SCHEMA AND k.INDEX_NAME=i.INDEX_NAME AND i.TABLE_SCHEMA=c.TABLE_SCHEMA AND i.TABLE_NAME=c.TABLE_NAME AND k.COLUMN_NAME=c.COLUMN_NAME AND i.IS_UNIQUE = 'D' AND i.TABLE_SCHEMA = :SCHEMA AND i.TABLE_NAME = :TABLE ORDER BY k.ORDINAL_POSITION

SELECT i.INDEX_NAME INDEX_NAME, k.COLUMN_NAME COLUMN_NAME FROM QSYS2.SYSKEYS k, QSYS2.SYSINDEXES i, QSYS2.SYSCOLUMNS c WHERE k.INDEX_SCHEMA=i.INDEX_SCHEMA AND k.INDEX_NAME=i.INDEX_NAME AND i.TABLE_SCHEMA=c.TABLE_SCHEMA AND i.TABLE_NAME=c.TABLE_NAME AND k.COLUMN_NAME=c.COLUMN_NAME AND i.IS_UNIQUE = 'D' AND i.TABLE_SCHEMA = :SCHEMA AND i.TABLE_NAME = :TABLE ORDER BY k.ORDINAL_POSITION

SELECT c.CONSTRAINT_NAME CHECK_NAME, substr(k.CHECK_CLAUSE,1,100) CHECK_TXT, 1 CHECK_STATUS, '' CHECK_DESC FROM QSYS2.SYSCST c, QSYS2.SYSCHKCST k WHERE c.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA=k.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA AND c.CONSTRAINT_NAME=k.CONSTRAINT_NAME AND C.CONSTRAINT_TYPE='CHECK' AND c.CONSTRAINT_NAME not like 'QSYS_%' AND C.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA=:SCHEMA AND C.TABLE_NAME=:TABLE

select PK_TABLE.TABLE_NAME PK_TABLE_NAME, REF.CONSTRAINT_NAME FK_NAME, FK_TABLE.COLUMN_NAME FK_COLUMN_NAME, PK_TABLE.COLUMN_NAME PK_COLUMN_NAME from QSYS2.SYSREFCST as REF, QSYS2.SYSKEYCST as FK_TABLE, QSYS2.SYSKEYCST as PK_TABLE where REF.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = FK_TABLE.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and REF.CONSTRAINT_NAME = FK_TABLE.CONSTRAINT_NAME and REF.UNIQUE_CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = PK_TABLE.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and REF.UNIQUE_CONSTRAINT_NAME = PK_TABLE.CONSTRAINT_NAME and PK_TABLE.ORDINAL_POSITION = FK_TABLE.ORDINAL_POSITION and FK_TABLE.TABLE_NAME =:TABLE and FK_TABLE.TABLE_SCHEMA = :SCHEMA

select k.CONSTRAINT_NAME PK_NAME, c.COLUMN_NAME COLUMN_NAME from QSYS2.SYSCST k , QSYS2.SYSKEYCST c where k.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA = c.CONSTRAINT_SCHEMA and k.CONSTRAINT_NAME = c.CONSTRAINT_NAME and k.TABLE_SCHEMA = c.TABLE_SCHEMA and k.TABLE_NAME = c.TABLE_NAME and k.CONSTRAINT_TYPE = 'PRIMARY KEY' and k.TABLE_SCHEMA = :SCHEMA and k.TABLE_NAME = :TABLE order by k.CONSTRAINT_NAME, c.ORDINAL_POSITION
